'''Chalmian''' ({{lang-fa|<U+0686><U+0644><U+0645><U+064A><U+0627><U+0646>}}, also [[Romanize]]d as '''Chalm<U+012B><U+0101>n''')<ref>{{GEOnet3|11001670|Chalmian}}</ref> is a village in [[Hasan Reza Rural District]], in the [[Central District (Juybar County)|Central District]] of [[Juybar County]], [[Mazandaran Province]], [[Iran]]. At the 2006 census, its population was 219, in 56 families.<ref>{{IranCensus2006|02}}</ref>  

